@startuml worker_etcd_lease
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
title Worker etcd lease and cluster row Put

participant "EtcdClusterManager" as CM
participant "EtcdStore" as Store
participant "etcd Lease" as Lease
participant "etcd KV" as KV
participant "EtcdKeepAlive" as KA

== start InitKeepAlive ==
CM -> Store: InitKeepAlive
Store -> Store: keepAliveValue init
Store -> Store: LaunchKeepAliveThreads

== lease and first Put ==
Store -> Store: RunKeepAliveTask
Store -> Lease: LeaseGrant
Lease --> Store: leaseId
Store -> KA: EtcdKeepAlive Init
Store -> Store: AutoCreate
Store -> Store: keepAliveValue timestamp
Store -> KV: PutWithLeaseId
note right of Store
  value: timestamp;state;hostId
  optional: client_count
end note
KV --> Store: OK

== lease keepalive stream ==
loop renew
  KA -> Lease: LeaseKeepAlive
  Lease --> KA: renew TTL
end
note right of KA: stream does not update key value. use explicit Put to change value

== UpdateNodeState ==
CM -> Store: UpdateNodeState
Store -> Store: copy and set state
Store -> KV: PutWithLeaseId new value
KV --> Store: OK

== extension client count note ==
note over Store, KV
  ClientManager counts clients
  throttle then Put same lease
  Client parses GetAll for Po2
  RemoveClient/Disconnect on Worker also
  tears down URMA/UB for that C↔W session
  (see seq-urma-client-worker-lifecycle.puml)
end note

@enduml
